# Internal-only strategy / planning docs (never publish to the public repo).
# The whitepaper PRDs and the synthetic_handshake_protocol spec are public;
# anything under SNHP_Whitepaper/ ending in _STRATEGY.md, _INTERNAL.md, or
# starting with INTERNAL_ stays local-only.
SNHP_Whitepaper/*_STRATEGY.md
SNHP_Whitepaper/*_INTERNAL.md
SNHP_Whitepaper/INTERNAL_*
